The cause is that the IP address of the server is not reachable. linkFailed(6): FTP failed. The cause is connecting to server failed. authenticateFailed(7): FTP failed. The cause is authenticating failed.For FTP mode only. fileReadFailed(8): FTP failed. The cause is reading file failed. fileWriteFailed(9): FTP failed.
